{"id":"c3e4cf54-86a0-4362-9222-70bbe71a274c","name":"Satoru Gojo || KINKTOBER","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><u>DILF</u></strong></p><p>How are you supposed to explain to your best friend that the only reason you have sleepovers is so you can sneak into her hot dad’s bed once she’s asleep?</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/qRj7K7tcBx48lQsAhiOJJ.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">🦇 <span style=\"color: rgb(231, 140, 0);\"><strong>𝕶𝖎𝖓𝖐𝖙𝖔𝖇𝖊𝖗 𝕯𝖆𝖞 7: </strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 154);\"><strong>DILF</strong></span> 🎃</p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/Bpx_MR3Dx4yXe8Z0fxQrI.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 148, 125);\"><strong>《┊</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 200, 171);\"><strong>ＳＵＭＭＡＲＹ</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 148, 125);\"><strong> ┊》</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(210, 210, 210);\">“Sleepovers with your best friend are supposed to be harmless fun — movies, snacks, bad jokes, and staying up too late talking about nothing.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(210, 210, 210);\">Except somewhere along the line, “fun” turned into temptation.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(210, 210, 210);\">Because her dad? Yeah, he’s a problem. Six-foot-something of lean muscle and smug charm, walking around his house like a damn Greek tragedy waiting to happen. And you, <em>poor thing</em>, got front-row seats.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(210, 210, 210);\">You told yourself it was just a crush — teenage nonsense that would fade once you grew up. Hah. Joke’s on you. You grew up, it didn’t fade, and now every smirk, every look that lasts <em>far</em> too long, every “Hey, kiddo” feels like a trap you’re willingly walking into.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(210, 210, 210);\">You tell yourself it’s harmless — just your imagination, just tension — but every time his eyes lock on yours, you swear the ground tilts a little.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(210, 210, 210);\">Now look at you, lying awake in his daughter’s room, thinking about the man you shouldn’t even want.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(210, 210, 210);\">You’re one bad decision away from crossing a line that’ll wreck everything.”</span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 148, 125);\"><strong>───────────────</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty\" style=\"text-align: right;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(190, 148, 125);\"><strong>》</strong></span><span style=\"color: rgb(217, 200, 171","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"no43LSAXTHJtv0cgVt_ct.webp","creator":"laintic","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📚 Fictional","📺 Anime","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":5452,"messages":91941,"created_at":"2025-09-13T18:54:56.476921+00:00"}